Data.equation: faultTimerLogic.clock.y = faultTimerLogic.clock.offset+(if time < faultTimerLogic.clock.startTime then 0 else time-faultTimerLogic.clock.startTime);
step.y = step.offset+(if time < step.startTime then 0 else step.height);

G4CHIL.G1.avr.limiter1.y = smooth(0, (if G4CHIL.G1.avr.limiter1.u > G4CHIL.G1.avr.limiter1.uMax then G4CHIL.G1.avr.limiter1.uMax else (if G4CHIL.G1.avr.limiter1.u < G4CHIL.G1.avr.limiter1.uMin then G4CHIL.G1.avr.limiter1.uMin else G4CHIL.G1.avr.limiter1.u)));
